  "title": "Records Management Support Officer (6 months)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title: Records Management Support Officer (6 months)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Advert:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a detail-oriented Records Management Support Officer to join our Records Management Department. This role will focus on management of physical records.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities include:</strong></p><p><strong>System Management</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Assist in administration of digital records system (onboarding, file uploads, folder creation, access rights)<br />- Manage physical records inventory system and user access</p><p><strong>Physical Records Operations</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Oversee physical files operations and darts room (which houses physical files) including disposal requests, folder management, and digitised records access<br />- Conduct records appraisal and disposal exercise</p><p><strong>Compliance & Documentation</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Follow up on revisions needed in handbook<br />- Manage MOUs, Legal Deposits, and international agreements</p><p><strong>Support & Outreach</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Provide ongoing support to Records Champions and resolve queries<br />- Assist with records management outreach and communications initiatives<br />\n<strong>Requirements</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>At least diploma in business, information management, or related field<br />- Experience in records management, information management, or related field<br />- Strong organisational skills with attention to detail<br />- Proficiency in digital systems and databases<br />- Excellent communication and stakeholder management abilities<br />- Ability to work independently<br /></p><p>Job Salary: $20 to $22 per hour<br />Job Location: Newton<br />Jon Duration: 6 months (Start 23 February 2026)<br /></p><p>EA License No: 96C4864<br />Reg. No.: R24121728 EUNICE WOO JING QI</p>",
